
---

# 🚫 .gitignore (copy-paste ready)

```gitignore
# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/

# Jupyter Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Streamlit cache
.streamlit/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Model files (optional if you don't want to push)
*.joblib
*.pkl

# Logs
*.log

# VS Code settings
.vscode/